un|v2=Moon|area=[[Evolution|Evolve]] {{p|Sliggoo}}}}\n{{Availability/Entry2|v=Ultra Sun|v2=Ultra Moon|area=[[Evolution|Evolve]] {{p|Sliggoo}}}}\n|}\n|}\n{{Availability/Footer}}\n\n====In side games====\n{{Availability/Header|type=Dragon}}\n{{Availability/NA|gen=VI}}\n{{Availability/Gen|gen=VI}}\n{{Availability/Entry1|1|v=Battle Trozei|color={{defense color}}|area=[[Mountain of Order#Stage 4|Mountain of Order: Stage 4]]}}\n{{Availability/Entry1|1|v=Shuffle|color={{beauty color}}|area=[[Expert Stages|Expert Stage: Stage EX30]]}}\n{{Availability/Entry1|1|v=Rumble World|color={{fire color}}|area=[[Dark Land#Forgotten Forest|Dark Land: Forgotten Forest]] <small>(Back Boss)</small>}}\n{{Availability/Entry1|1|v=Picross|color={{skill color light}}|area=[[Pokémon Picross Stages#Area 27|Area 27: Stage 02]]}}\n|}\n|}\n{{Availability/Footer}}\n\n===Stats===\n====Base stats====\n{{BaseStats\n|type=dragon\n|HP=90\n|Attack=100\n|Defense=70\n|SpAtk=110\n|SpDef=150\n|Speed=80}}\n\n===Type effectiveness===\n{{TypeEffectiveness\n|type1=Dragon\n|Normal=  100\n|Flying=  100\n|Fighting=100\n|Ground=  100\n|Rock=    100\n|Bug=     100\n|Poison=  100\n|Ghost=   100\n|Steel=   100\n|Fire=     50\n|Water=    50\n|Grass=    50\n|Electric= 50\n|Psychic= 100\n|Ice=     200\n|Dragon=  200\n|Dark=    100\n|Fairy=   200\n|notes=yes\n|sapsipper=maybe}}\n\n===Learnset===\n====By [[Level|leveling up]]====\n{{learnlist/levelh/7|Goodra|Dragon|Dragon|6}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Aqua Tail|Water|Physical|90|90|10}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Outrage|Dragon|Physical|120|100|10||\'\'\'}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Feint|Normal|Physical|30|100|10}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Tackle|Normal|Physical|40|100|35}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Bubble|Water|Special|40|100|30}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Absorb|Grass|Special|20|100|25}}\n{{learnlist/level7|1|Protect|Normal|Status|—|—|10}}\n{{learnlist/level7|{{tt|Evo.|Learned upon evolving}}|Aqua Tail|Water|Physical|90|90|10}}\n{{learnlist/level7|5|Absorb|Grass|Special|20|100|25}}\n{{learnlist/